com.steffbeard.totalwar.modules.crops.listener

Class GrowListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.steffbeard.totalwar.modules.crops.listener.GrowListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.bukkit.event.Listener

    public class GrowListener
extends Object
implements org.bukkit.event.Listener
    Event listener for all plant growth related events. Whenever a crop, plant block, or sapling attempts to grow, its type is checked against the biomes in which it is permitted to grow. If the biome is not permitted, the event is canceled and the plant does not grow. Additionally, all instances of bonemeal being used as fertilizer are canceled.
    Author:
    WildWeazel
